WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.820 --> 00:00:03.310
<v ->Hi, my name is Christina and I'm from Germany.

2
00:00:03.310 --> 00:00:07.050
My question is what is the best way to learn English?

3
00:00:07.050 --> 00:00:08.540
Well, I was really lucky because

4
00:00:08.540 --> 00:00:11.600
I lived abroad in New Zealand for one year,

5
00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:14.890
so I've spoken a lot of English there

6
00:00:14.890 --> 00:00:16.410
and I really improved my English.

7
00:00:16.410 --> 00:00:18.580
But what is really, really important

8
00:00:18.580 --> 00:00:22.150
before you do that is that you learn some basics.

9
00:00:22.150 --> 00:00:25.510
So I learned the basics at school with a lot of listening

10
00:00:25.510 --> 00:00:28.590
and with a lot of reading, so exactly

11
00:00:28.590 --> 00:00:30.770
what those kind of videos are for.

12
00:00:30.770 --> 00:00:32.170
So I think it's a good combination

13
00:00:32.170 --> 00:00:33.830
if you first do the basic stuff

14
00:00:33.830 --> 00:00:35.470
and then you just go overhat

15
00:00:35.470 --> 00:00:38.073
and just try to speak English all the time.
